Generate product and content catalogs for pacifichome_global

productcatalog:
 - english
    - subset created when generating pacifichome 'full' product catalog
    - copy that as-is
 - german
    - translate the english subset to german(de) using openAI

contentcatalog:
 - english
    - subset created when generating pacifichome 'full' content catalog
    - copy that as-is
 - german
    - translate the english subset to german(de) using openAI

